Rest is representational state transfer. It is an architectural style.

Restful Web services : Consider a sample social media application

1 User ---> * posts


operations performed : 

-- Retrieve all users : GET /users

-- Create a user : POST /users

-- Retrieve one user : GET /users/{userid}

-- Delete a user : DELETE /users/{userid}


-- Retrieve all posts for a user : GET /users/{userid}/posts

-- create a post for a user : POST /users/{userid}/posts

-- retrieve details for a post : GET /users/{userid}/posts/{postid}